1464
01:34:40,074 --> 01:34:43,237
- Mr. Biegler.
- I'm a bachelor, Your Honor.

1465
01:34:43,344 --> 01:34:46,074
That's a great help.
Mr. Dancer?

1466
01:34:46,180 --> 01:34:51,049
I was overseas during the war.
I learned a French word.

1467
01:34:51,152 --> 01:34:53,416
I'm afraid that might be
slightly suggestive.

1468
01:34:53,521 --> 01:34:55,512
Most French words are.

1469
01:34:55,623 --> 01:34:58,956
All right, gentlemen,
back to your places.

1470
01:34:59,060 --> 01:35:03,963
For the benefit of the jury, but more
especially for the spectators...

1471
01:35:04,065 --> 01:35:07,967
the undergarment referred to
in the testimony was, to be exact...

1472
01:35:08,069 --> 01:35:09,798
Mrs. Manion's panties.

1473
01:35:14,008 --> 01:35:17,774
I wanted you to get your snickering
over and done with.

1474
01:35:17,878 --> 01:35:22,144
This pair of panties will be mentioned
again in the course of this trial.

1475
01:35:22,249 --> 01:35:25,844
And when it happens, there will not be
one laugh, one snicker...

1476
01:35:25,953 --> 01:35:29,821
one giggle or even one smirk
in my courtroom.

1477
01:35:29,924 --> 01:35:33,519
There isn't anything comic
about a pair of panties...

1478
01:35:33,627 --> 01:35:37,119
which figure in the violent death
of one man...

1479
01:35:37,231 --> 01:35:41,429
and the possible incarceration
of another.

1480
01:35:41,535 --> 01:35:43,264
Proceed, Mr. Biegler.

1481
01:35:43,370 --> 01:35:45,497
