1485
01:35:54,648 --> 01:35:57,674
I gave her a lie detector test
at her request.

1486
01:35:57,785 --> 01:36:01,277
Now after all this investigation,
did you believe Mrs. Manion?

1487
01:36:01,388 --> 01:36:03,879
- I did.
