1495
01:36:25,746 --> 01:36:29,739
In any case, you yourself
in your own heart and mind...

1496
01:36:29,850 --> 01:36:32,478
are quite convinced
of Mrs. Manion's honesty?

1497
01:36:32,586 --> 01:36:35,146
- Yes, sir.
