wanted everyone else to believe it too.

1507
01:37:07,488 --> 01:37:09,388
One moment, please.

1508
01:37:13,127 --> 01:37:15,721
Ask him in what manner she swore.

1509
01:37:15,830 --> 01:37:19,129
Did Mrs. Manion say how
she had sworn to her husband?

1510
01:37:19,233 --> 01:37:23,169
Yes, sir. She said
