1511
01:37:23,270 --> 01:37:28,105
This lane in the woods,
what's it used for, where does it go?

1512
01:37:28,209 --> 01:37:31,406
It used to be a logging road.
It doesn't go anyplace, just stops.

1513
01:37:31,512 --> 01:37:33,412
Who uses it now?

1514
01:37:33,514 --> 01:37:35,744
I think it's a road
kids drive down to park.

1515
01:37:35,850 --> 01:37:38,478
- You mean it's a lovers' lane?
- I think so.

1516
01:37:38,586 --> 01:37:41,453
- The witness is yours.
- No more questions.

1517
01:37:41,555 --> 01:37:44,991
- The witness may step down.
- In view of evidence concerning rape...

1518
01:37:45,092 --> 01:37:47,253
which Your Honor
has ruled admissible...

1519
01:37:47,361 --> 01:37:49,591
the prosecution asks for
a 30-minute recess...

1520
01:37:49,697 --> 01:37:52,689
in order to bring in another witness
we had not anticipated using?

1521
01:37:52,800 --> 01:37:55,496
All right.
We'll take a 30-minute recess.

1522
01:37:55,603 --> 01:37:57,093
Recess.

1523
01:38:04,044 --> 01:38:06,478
Why didn't you tell me
