1526
01:38:14,488 --> 01:38:18,390
It might have looked like something
else... like I didn't believe her.

1527
01:38:19,860 --> 01:38:24,729
- How much more didn't you tell me?
- We told you everything else.

1528
01:38:24,832 --> 01:38:26,857
Is that right, Laura?

1529
01:38:26,967 --> 01:38:29,128
Oh, yes, everything else.

1530
01:38:29,236 --> 01:38:31,397
