1539
01:39:18,686 --> 01:39:21,655
They wanted me to make a test
for the presence of sperm...

1540
01:39:21,755 --> 01:39:24,121
on the person
of a Mrs. Frederick Manion.

1541
01:39:24,224 --> 01:39:28,024
